title: Rada and K
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, International, Organic, Juice bar, Delivery
description: A cozy welcoming vegetarian cafe, with a homey ambiance, is located in the heart of the city. Has plenty of vegan options. Operates a clean kitchen/cafe. Does not use microwaves. Uses Russian live foods and natural spices. Conducts workshops, events, film screenings, video seminars. Owners do not smoke or drink. Pet friendly.
